# Project bootstrap (direnv).
#
# Pulls the project-pinned toolchain from mise.toml (go, task,
# bazelisk, clang, air, ...) plus the [env] block (PATH addition,
# GOBIN, BIGQUERY_EMULATOR_HOST, ...) into this shell. Without this,
# only globally-activated mise tools end up on PATH and per-project
# pins / env vars are ignored.
#
# First time on this checkout, run `mise install` (or
# `task tools:install` once `task` is on PATH) to fetch the pinned
# versions.

if has mise; then
  eval "$(mise env -s bash)"
fi
